The wireframe shows a simple layout for a restaurant website. Here's a breakdown of the layout mapping to semantic HTML: 1. **Header/Nav Items**: The top navigation bar includes links labeled "Home," "Menu," "Pre-order," "Reservation," and "Contact Us." These can be represented using `
` elements. 2. **Hero Structure**: There is no distinct hero section visible in the wireframe, but the main content area could serve as a hero-like introduction to the restaurant's offerings. 3. **Content Blocks**: The main content area is divided into four sections: "Starters," "Main Course," "Desserts," and "Beverages." Each section has a title, a brief description, and a button labeled "Explore Menu." 4. **Footer**: The footer contains a copyright notice stating "© Delicious Restaurant 2022." **Layout Choices**: - The layout uses a grid layout for arranging the content blocks. - The grid is likely implemented using CSS Grid or Flexbox for better responsiveness across different devices. - Responsive design considerations include ensuring that the content blocks adjust their size and position based on screen width. **Assumptions**: - The "Explore Menu" buttons will likely lead to a detailed menu page when clicked. - The layout assumes a desktop view initially, with mobile responsiveness handled through media queries. ```html Delicious Restaurant
Home Menu Pre-order Reservation Contact Us

Starters

Treat your tastebuds with our exquisite starters that prepare you for the main course.

Main Course

Indulge in our variety of main course options - From traditional fare to fusion dishes.

Desserts

Savor our delicious desserts that will leave you craving for more.

Beverages

Quench your thirst with our refreshing and unique beverages.

© Delicious Restaurant 2022

```

The wireframe depicts a simple webpage layout for a social media management service. Here's a breakdown of the layout and its mapping to semantic HTML: 1. **Header/Nav**: - The top bar contains the company name "Social Media ManageR" on the left. - Navigation links ("Home", "About", "Services", "Pricing", "Contact") are aligned to the right. 2. **Hero Section**: - Positioned below the header, it features a large image placeholder on the right side. - Text on the left promotes the services offered by the company. 3. **Content Blocks**: - Two distinct sections follow the hero: "Our Services" and "Pricing". - Each section has a heading and a brief description. 4. **Footer**: - At the bottom, it includes copyright information and navigation links similar to the header. 5. **Layout Choices**: - The layout uses a grid layout for the hero section, with the image on the right and text on the left. - The content blocks use a flexbox layout to align the headings and descriptions vertically. - Responsive design is assumed, given the layout's adaptability across different screen sizes. 6. **Responsiveness**: - The layout is designed to be responsive, ensuring that the hero image scales appropriately and the content blocks remain readable on smaller screens. 7. **Assumptions**: - The placeholder image will be replaced with actual content. - The text within the hero section will be optimized for readability and SEO. - The navigation links will be functional and lead to the respective pages. ```html Social Media ManageR

Social Media ManageR

Home About Services Pricing Contact

Optimize Your Social Media Growth

Unlock the power of Social Media with our services

Our Services

Boost your reach, Increase your engagement, Analyze your data

Pricing

Starting at just $100 per month

© 2023 Social Media ManageR

Home About Services Pricing Contact
``` ```
